data.name: description3.Text
data.value: A captivating floral boxed design that can transform your Christmas into a winter wonderland. Our latest White Christmas box combines an arrangement of Green Mini Murrayas, White Cotton Flowers and White Button Poms. Gift this to your loved ones as a symbol of purity and spirit of the season.

data.name: description8.Text
data.value: Inspired by the fantasy world of Beauty and The Beast, the Enchanted Rose flower box comes with the most stunning single preserved red rose. A delicate rose, immaculate to the eye, preserved to maintain its natural beauty, texture, and soft red petals.

data.name: description7.Text
data.value: Bask in the light of our Sunday Sunflower arrangement - a bouquet brimming with purple statice flowers, soi, and papua leaves, with a bright golden sunflower right in between. Send this beautiful flower bouquet to someone, and brighten up their day.

data.name: description1.Text
data.value: A serene arrangement of delicate blooms and soothing hues, that offer a graceful tribute to honor their memory. Express your heartfelt sympathies and give their loved ones a memento of solace, with our ethereal Clement Whisper Funeral Basket.

data.name: description10.Text
data.value: An exquisite wreath stand, elegantly adorned with blooms reminiscent of precious pearls, pays homage to cherished memories and offers a comforting gesture of sympathy. Symbolizing both solace and remembrance, our Pearl Wreath stands as a perfect tribute to those deeply missed.
